MONGODB DATABASE:
------------------
MYSQL-RELATIONAL DATABASE: TABLES
MONGODB: NO-SQL DATABASE: KEY:VALUE PAIR
--mongodb is open source
--mongodb is applicable where graph,trees,documentation
--In mongodb table is treated collection
-- in each collection,an individual record called as document.
-- in mongodb primary key is automatically generated by the database
--mongodb is scalable
--mongodb stores the data in the form of JSON or key:value pair
--JSON format is very popular to transmit data between any two electrons and API data formats Through HTTP.
--It is case-sensitive
--in mongodb we perform crud operations(ddl and dml in sql)

